Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 04 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Esophagus' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Dilatation' radio button is enabled
And 'Stenosis' radio button is enabled
And 'Calibre change' radio button is enabled
And 'Mass' radio button is enabled
And 'Diverticula' radio button is enabled
And 'Duplication cyst' radio button is enabled
And 'Varices' radio button is enabled
And 'Axial hiatus hernia' radio button is enabled
And 'Paraesophageal hernia' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Stenosis' radio button
Then 'Upper 1/3' radio button is enabled
And 'Average 1/3' radio button is enabled
And 'Lower 1/3' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Mass' radio button
Then 'Upper 1/3' radio button is enabled
And 'Average 1/3' radio button is enabled
And 'Lower 1/3' radio button is enabled
And 'Maximum wall thickness' input field is enabled
And 'Maximum craniocaudal extension' input field is enabled

When I select 'Paraesophageal hernia' radio button
Then 'Upside-down stomach' checkbox is enabled
